Text:
Audio quality is total sh!t.
sounds like it was recorded off an AM radio, using a cheap tape-deck.  Then audio captured at 24kpbs and up-sampled to 256.

Don't Waste Your Time!

I concur with waltt2's comment.

Pretty sure this is a recording of AM radio then burnt to a vinyl record, which was then scratched with a piece of sharp metal, and played on a CD player. Shit!
